```{r setup, include=FALSE}
knitr::opts_chunk$set(echo = TRUE)
```

```{r}
dataset <- read.csv("Data/Data - DS C1 Course.csv")
```

```{r}
is.na(dataset)
```

```{r}
ggplot(dataset, aes(x= Age, y= Which.City.are.you.currently.residing.in.))+
  geom_point()
```
```{r}
dataset %>% select(Age) %>% n_distinct()
```

```{r}
ggplot(dataset, aes(x= Age, y= Gender))+
  geom_bar(stat = "identity")
```

```{r}
dataset %>% group_by(dataset$Do.you.understand.that.this.is.a.paid.course..) %>% count()
```

```{r}
ggplot(dataset, aes(x= Do.you.understand.that.this.is.a.paid.course.., y= Gender))+
  geom_bar(stat = "identity")  
```
